    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Your can effectively attack and defend with your gauntlet.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Shielded Gauntlet Attack, Shield Gauntlet Style, Weapon Focus (gauntlet or spiked gauntlet), proficiency with bucklers and light shields.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>While using Shield Gauntlet Style, you no longer lose your shield bonus to AC when you attack with your gauntlet (or spiked gauntlet) or use it to hold a weapon. In addition, you add your gauntlet's enhancement bonus to the shield bonus to AC granted by this feat as if it were a shield enhancement bonus.",
